Ask HN: Part-time software engineering opportunities?
text:
Hey folks, do part-time software engineering roles (~20h of work) exist? Where would you find such jobs advertised?

For context - I worked as a software engineer in the past six years and took a career break this past December due to burning out of the job. I am looking to ease my way in by working part-time as an engineer, but I couldn't find such postings online anywhere.

Ask HN: Should I pull (some) cash out of BofA?
text:

That said; should I pull out ~$20k in cash to cover living expenses or emergencies?
